b) Compensation for damage in accordance with law;

c) Recommendations, complaints, denunciations and lawsuits about acts violations of the law by organizations and individuals that are granted a decision on recognition of circulation or self-declaration of circulation of plant varieties.

2. Organizations and individuals using plant varieties have the following obligations: 

a) Comply with the production process announced by the organization or individual that has registered the grant of a decision on recognition of circulation or self-declaration of circulation of the plant variety;

b) When an incident occurs or detecting bad consequences caused by plant varieties, they must promptly notify organizations and individuals providing plant varieties and local authorities for handling.

Luật Trồng trọt@33:
Rights and obligations of organizations and individuals registering to grant Decision on recognition of first-class plants, Decision on recognition of first-class orchards

1. Organizations and individuals under registration name issue a decision on recognition of leading varieties, a decision on recognition of a leading orchard with the right to exploit or authorize organizations and individuals to exploit propagating materials for production and trading purposes.

2 Organizations and individuals that register for the issuance of the Decision on recognition of leading varieties and the Decision on recognition of leading orchards have the following obligations: ;

