đ) Accept part or all of the lawsuit claim, declare an cancellation of part or the whole of the settlement decision settle complaints about illegal competition case-handling decisions; compel the agency or person competent to issue a decision to settle a complaint about a decision on handling a competition case to re-settle the case in accordance with the Competition Law;

