c) In the case of a judgment , if the Court's decision has canceled the disciplinary decision on dismissal, the disciplinary decision on dismissal is no longer valid. The head of an agency or organization that has issued a disciplinary decision on dismissal must implement the court's judgment or decision; If the judgment debtor has performed the administrative act is illegal, the judgment debtor must stop performing such administrative act from the date of receiving the court's judgment or decision; If the judgment debtor's act of failure to perform his/her duties or official duties is illegal, the judgment debtor must perform his/her duties or official duties as prescribed by law from the date of receipt of the judgment or decision of the Court. Court;

